      "text": "Complete Key Reference"
    },
    {
      "type": "prose",
      "text": "An alphabetical-ish reference of every Normal-mode key. For prefixed commands (those starting with {key:g}, {key:z}, {key:[}, {key:]}, {key:Ctrl-W}), see the dedicated overview topics in [Part 15](#prefixes.g-overview)."
    },
